						<summary>

						<p>Hero-stone (No. 8) set up in a field to the west of the village.</p>						

						<p>Circa 10th century.</p>						

						<p>This badly damaged record seems to register the death of an individual during a cattle-raid. Māchemarāja set up the stone.</p>						

